author: Michael Chen
title: 'AL East clinched, killin' it!': Blue Jays fans celebrate division title win
text:
A A Fans awoke to news of their baseball team clinching the American League East division title as champions Thursday morning. This title win ends 22 years of frustration which fans and the Jays players faced since the team last won the back-to-back World Series titles in 1993.
The fans shared their photos, videos and thoughts on the 15-2 victory on Twitter and Instagram as seen below.
